T02TD2741E:127b-1: aashtotta r'a sa ta a'ary'a ba lo ke te shva ra s'a dha nam /
T02TD2741E:127b-3: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gi sgrub thabs brgya rtsa brgyad pa//
T02TD2741E:127b-4: rje btsun thugs rje chen po spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2741E:127b-5: gang gis chogs gnyis rab bsags pas //
T02TD2741E:127b-6: de nyid zab mo mngon gzigs te //
T02TD2741E:127b-7: brtse bas 'gro la sna tshogs thabs //
T02TD2741E:127b-9: stong nyid snying rje las byung ba //
T02TD2741E:127b-10: rnam lnga byang chub che bdag nyid //
T02TD2741E:127b-11: sku gsung thugs kyi thugs dag pa //
T02TD2741E:127b-12: 'jig rten mgon po mkhas pas sgrub //
T02TD2741E:127b-13: padmo zla dbus gzhon nu'i sku //
T02TD2741E:127b-14: skyil krung phyed brkyang 'gying bag brtan //
T02TD2741E:127b-15: zla ba rgyas pa'i zhal mdzes las //
T02TD2741E:127b-16: sa gsum bdag gir mdzad gzigs pa'o//
T02TD2741E:127b-17: mchog sbyin padmo'i g-yas dang g-yon //
T02TD2741E:127b-18: rgyal ba'i cod pan rin chen brgyan //
T02TD2741E:127b-19: 'od dpag med kyis spyi gtsug mdzes //
T02TD2741E:127b-20: de yi thugs ni padmar rgyas //
T02TD2741E:127b-22: sa gsum sbyong mdzad yi ge bzhi //
T02TD2741E:127b-23: 'khor lo rnam gsum dam tshig bzhi //
T02TD2741E:127b-25: thugs rje chen bo kharsa p'a na'i sgrub thabs tshigs su bcas pa bzhi pa rdzogs so//
